{"tid":1697811,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［法院陷家產］韓正下達指令要求三權合作，為止暴制亂整頓司法機關！","createTime":"2019-11-07T05:34:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T13:13:13.000Z","uid":219007,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"612f1eea90225cb7963122f735f9059ff5c0e8eb","tid":1697811,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T05:34:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/lhDz6UOgaQU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FlhDz6UOgaQU&d=40Eeu%2FLL1847%2FNonScroNXs01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=c53e0c63\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/lhDz6UOgaQU</a><br />\n毓民：若果之後有示威者告唔入，法官會開始有壓力。普通法好快玩完，已經唔係換個特首就可以解決嘅問題。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n終審法院首席法官和終審法院其他法官，根據司法人員推薦委員會推薦，由香港特別行政區（香港特區）行政長官任命。<br />\n根據《基本法》，終審法院首席法官和終審法院其他法官的任命，須由行政長官徴得立法會同意，並報中華人民共和國全國人民代表大會常務委員會（全國人大常委會）。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&lsquo;<em><span style=\"color: blue;\">韓正稱，止暴制亂、恢復秩序是香港社會目前最重要的工作，也是行政、立法、司法機關的共同責任和最大共識</span></em>&rsquo; <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20191106/s00001/1573014743564/接見林鄭月娥-韓正-香港極端暴力活動任何國家都不能容忍【短片】\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20191106%2Fs00001%2F1573014743564%2F%E6%8E%A5%E8%A6%8B%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%9C%88%E5%A8%A5-%E9%9F%93%E6%AD%A3-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%A5%B5%E7%AB%AF%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E6%B4%BB%E5%8B%95%E4%BB%BB%E4%BD%95%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E9%83%BD%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E5%AE%B9%E5%BF%8D%E3%80%90%E7%9F%AD%E7%89%87%E3%80%91&d=40Eeu%2FLL1847%2FNonScroNXs01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=17109bf2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20191106%2Fs00001%2F1573014743564%2F%E6%8E%A5%E8%A6%8B%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%9C%88%E5%A8%A5-%E9%9F%93%E6%AD%A3-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%A5%B5%E7%AB%AF%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E6%B4%BB%E5%8B%95%E4%BB%BB%E4%BD%95%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E9%83%BD%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E5%AE%B9%E5%BF%8D%E3%80%90%E7%9F%AD%E7%89%87%E3%80%91&h=5267099e\" 